{"tid":1785492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拒絕入境大陸揮手區","createTime":"2019-12-16T11:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T00:58:19.000Z","uid":264809,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"840ba0a684c9a194d3e42d28d51b215579220140","tid":1785492,"uid":264809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"9月尾入境被拒絕入境，人面識別failed，之後兩個公安捉你入房用膊頭Cam拍住你，收走你回鄉證，全程無對話無查行李，15-20分鐘之後通知你拒絕入境。<br />\n<br />\n1.無原因<br />\n2.危害國家安全<br />\n3.出境入境邊防管理條例第八條第七項<br />\n<br />\n七)國務院公安部門、國家安全部門通知不准出境、入境的； <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我估而家全港起碼上萬人被拒入境，入境fail tg group已經有成差唔多40人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f46c49d769ffe8736f632d01d0f2dab31408167","tid":1785492,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"元旦倒數。。年年都係10、9、8、7、6。。。。。<br />\n今年，香港人在全球傳媒鏡頭下，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">10、9、光、復、香、港、時、代、革、命</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.22  聲援新疆集會<br />\n12.24 和你shop 我要攬炒<br />\n12.31 十八區和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1  元旦遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kn972fL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkn972fL.jpg&h=d7d2f971&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6TArHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6TArHq.jpg&h=46d9221e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFstMHt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFst